164
00:09:47,260 --> 00:09:50,310
But China took a moment
to celebrate the 70th anniversary

165
00:09:50,330 --> 00:09:54,290
of the Communist Party coming to power
and they did it in some style.

166
00:09:55,350 --> 00:09:58,360
